  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "nbgrader": {
     "grade": true,
     "grade_id": "cell-4a-statement-II-answer",
     "locked": false,
     "points": 1,
     "schema_version": 2,
     "solution": true
    }
   },
   "source": [
    "**SOLUTION:** \n",
    "**True**.\n",
    "\t\t\t$$ \\sum_{i=1}^{n} x_1 = \\underbrace{x_1 + x_1 + ... + x_1}_{n \\text{ times}} = nx_1 $$"
   ]
